messages.message:
The demo to eng-staff was very well received today. The 10 min slot stretched for the entire 30 minute meeting duration.
I had another meeting later in the day on GA planning with all parts of sales + marketing + legal - everyone is quite excited for this!

Reorganized the TODO with all the items for this next week.

One learning from today, the sales folks are quite conservative and customers are apparently even more.
We need to move first toward feature parity and after that towards performance improvement.
Hence, removing process files will be the last item. @Weiming Wu can start working on that as a separate branch once existing items are completed.
The code is now live on aihub-sandbox. Unfortunately there is a bug that leads to no fields being extracted :confused: @Abhishek Adupa is looking into this.
